LOUXOR FOR PETS 
The Baccarat Louxor for Pets Collection showcases the enchanting blend of artistry and charm in an array of pet accessories. Each piece reflects the Maison’s dedication to craftsmanship and detail. 

Adorned with customizable stainless-steel octagons and intricate diamond-cut crystal motifs, the collection transforms everyday moments with your four-legged friend into celebrations of elegance and companionship.

@Baccarat, bringing pleasure into the world of our four-legged friends.
